    @Description(value="JMS\uc758 ConnectionFactory\uc758 Resource\ub97c \ub098\ud0c0\ub0b4\ub294 MBean\uc774\ub2e4.\uc774 MBean\uc744 \ud1b5\ud574 \ud574\ub2f9\ud558\ub294 JMS ConnectionFactory\uc758 \uc815\ubcf4\ub97c \uc5bb\uc744 \uc218 \uc788\ub2e4.")
public interface JMSConnectionFactoryResourceMBean
extends jeus.management.j2ee.J2EEResourceMBean, jeus.management.j2ee.StateManageable
    JMS의 ConnectionFactory의 Resource를 나타내는 MBean이다.

    이 MBean을 통해 해당하는 JMS ConnectionFactory의 정보를 얻을 수 있다.
